.el .ds Aq '
.TH rom-weaver-tools-ppf-undo 1  "rom-weaver-tools-ppf-undo "
.SH NAME
rom\-weaver\-tools\-ppf\-undo \- Restore a ROM using undo data embedded in a PPF3 patch
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBrom\-weaver tools ppf\-undo\fR [\fB\-\-json\fR] <\fB\-o\fR|\fB\-\-output\fR> [\fB\-\-progress\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-progress\fR] [\fB\-\-trace\fR] [\fB\-\-dep\-trace\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIROM\fR> <\fIPPF\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Restore a ROM using undo data embedded in a PPF3 patch
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-json\fR
Emit progress and terminal status as JSON lines
.TP
\fB\-o\fR, \fB\-\-output\fR \fI<PATH>\fR
Output path for the restored ROM
.TP
\fB\-\-progress\fR
Force running progress events on
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-progress\fR
Disable running progress events
.TP
\fB\-\-trace\fR
Enable trace logs (also enabled by ROM_WEAVER_LOG or RUST_LOG)
.TP
\fB\-\-dep\-trace\fR
Enable trace logs from dependencies (for example nod)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fIROM\fR>
ROM produced by applying the PPF patch
.TP
<\fIPPF\fR>
PPF3 patch containing undo data
